description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 2.0 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Commercial Fryers that are effective as of April 22, 2011. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=fryers.pr_crit_fryers
